gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Trail Blazers 107, Grizzlies 100
gameRecap.excerpt: Portland completes the comeback and defeats Memphis in OT, 107-100. For Portland, Anfernee Simons led the way with 30 points (four 3PM), seven rebounds, and seven assists while aided by Jabari Walker adding 18 points and 12 rebounds in the victory. Santi Aldama tallied 21 points (five 3PM) and eight rebounds with Vince Williams Jr. putting up 21 points (four 3PM), eight rebounds, and two steals for Memphis in the losing effort. Portland improves to 17-42 on the season, while Memphis moves to 20-41 with the loss.
